########Compiling########
chasm should be compiled using a standard C++ compiler. The GNU C++
Compiler (G++) of the GNU Compiler Collection (GCC) is strongly
recommended. chasm.cpp (the primary file) should be in the same
directory as the header files when compiling.

G++ Command Example:
    g++ chasm.cpp -o chasm

For more information on compiling, see the included manual.

